{"type":"message","id":"caded3ea","parentId":"ded677a7","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:22:08.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the openclaw workspace directory but the file `OpenClaw-v2026.4.14-完整功能框架.md` is not there. The file may not exist or may be in a different location.\n\nLet me inform the user that I cannot find the specific file they're referring to. The file might:\n1. Not exist anymore (deleted/unmounted)\n2. Be in a different WSL distro or location\n3. Need to be re-saved to a accessible location\n\nI should ask the user to either provide the file path again or share the content directly.","thinkingSignature":"815a224780790f05e42038bc9c9ed6a932941b21b880eda934fb528ad0f9729d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n找不到该文件。搜索结果：\n\n- `\\\\wsl.localhost\\Ubuntu-20.04\\` 挂载在 `/mnt/wsl/docker-desktop-bind-mounts/Ubuntu-20.04/`\n- `.openclaw/workspace` 目录存在：`projects/-home-ai--openclaw-workspace/`\n- 但里面只有 `.jsonl` 文件，**没有 `main` 子目录**\n- 也没有 `OpenClaw-v2026.4.14-完整功能框架.md` 这个文件\n\n**可能原因**：\n1. Ubuntu-20.04 WSL 实例未运行或已停止\n2. 该文件在你重装 OpenClaw 前就已经丢失\n3. 文件在 `main` 目录之外的其他位置\n\n**解决方案**：\n1. 重新启动 Ubuntu-20.04 WSL 实例后再试\n2. 或者直接把这个文件的内容粘贴过来，我来做对比分析"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22950,"output":308,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44896,"cost":{"input":0.006885,"output":0.0003696,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00855288}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776428520099,"responseId":"063158e6218c6810107942f7e08ec445"}}
