{"type":"message","id":"15d086a3","parentId":"5c84f905","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:30:55.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'm getting a much clearer picture. Let me trace the architecture:\n\n1. **context-api** (port 3101 in code, but trying to use 3106) - This is a context compression/management service. Its default port is 3101 but it's configured to run on 3106.\n\n2. **proxy** - This is a reverse proxy that handles routing. It has `classify` and `score` methods from a `v8Client`. It uses `@isaced/ai-router`.\n\n3. **openclaw-listener** - connects to gateway via WebSocket, processes messages, uses intent/score APIs\n\nSo the intended architecture from the old system was:\n\n\n- Gateway on port 3100\n- proxy (v8Client) on some port handling intent/score/routing\n- context-api on 3101/3106 for context management\n- scene-classifier on 3105 for scene classification\n\nBut the current system has gateway on 18789, v8.TaskOrchestrator on 3103 for scoring, scene-classifier on 3105, and context-api crashing on 3106. The proxy that was supposed to route between these components isn't running as a service at all.\n\nI think the real problem is that when openclaw was reinstalled, it didn't preserve the custom service architecture from the v2026.4.14 document—the listener and proxy services weren't re-created or pointed to the wrong endpoints. So the cron jobs that depend on them are failing, and the whole routing layer is broken.\n\nLooking at what actually needs fixing: the context-api keeps crashing because something else is using port 3106, the wiki-learn cron is throwing a 401 error on some API call, the ephemeral-to-entity memory promotion isn't running, and there's probably no session-summary hook being triggered. I need to identify which services are actually supposed to be running and get them pointing to the right ports.","thinkingSignature":"07f1846a29dfb2d1e9f6b66ba7cc0494c86b199d71c861a95abc5ec80f6ca70c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wrs17djr6w89_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 session-summary hook 是否存在且被正确触发\ncat ~/.openclaw/hooks/session-summary/HOOK.md 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\n# 检查 ephemeral 最近写入\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/ephemeral/2026-04-17-12.jsonl 2>/dev/null | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52922,"output":502,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75062,"cost":{"input":0.015876599999999998,"output":0.0006024,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017777279999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429043567,"responseId":"06315af14a08d1c67ca516a95667f1e3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"16e89033","parentId":"15d086a3","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:30:55.917Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_wrs17djr6w89_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取刚结束的 session 内容。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": {\n        \"bins\": [\"node\"],\n        \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"]\n      },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成刚结束 session 的结构化摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n- **异步执行**：hook 立即返回，摘要生成在后台，不阻塞命令响应\n- **降级策略**：LLM 不可用或生成失败时，写入规则摘要，不报错不中断\n- **文件格式**：`memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`，带 `<!-- summary-only -->` 标记\n\n## 摘要格式\n\n```markdown\n# Session: {date} {time}\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 摘要\n## 主题\n{一句话概括，少于20字}\n\n## AI 决策模式\n{基于 scene/score/strategy 数据分析，1-3句描述}\n\n## 关键决策\n{决策列表，没有则写\"无明确决策\"}\n\n## 重要发现\n{发现列表，没有则写\"无\"}\n\n## 待跟进\n{待办列表，没有则写\"无\"}\n\n<!-- source: {sessionKey} -->\n```\n\n### AI 决策模式分析\n\n摘要 prompt 新增决策模式分析，从 ephemeral 的 v8 决策数据（scene、score、recommendedStrategy、risk factor）提炼：\n- 主要场景类型（clarify/task/troubleshoot/chat/...）\n- 复杂度评分分布\n- 推荐策略分布（DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA）\n- 风险意识表现\n- 互动风格（主动/被动/谨慎/大胆）\n\n## LLM 调用\n\n通过 v8 Router (3102) 调用 LLM 生成摘要，超时 20s。\n\n## Bootstrap 读取\n\nsession 启动时，扫描 `memory/` 下最新摘要文件（按修改时间），读入作为上下文。\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":246,"aggregated":"---\nname: session-summary\ndescription: \"session 结束时（/new 或 /reset）生成结构化摘要，写入 memory/，供下次 bootstrap 读取。依赖 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取刚结束的 session 内容。\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\": {\n      \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n      \"events\": [\"command:new\", \"command:reset\"],\n      \"requires\": {\n        \"bins\": [\"node\"],\n        \"config\": [\"workspace.dir\"]\n      },\n      \"always\": true\n    }\n  }\n---\n\n# session-summary\n\n每次 `/new` 或 `/reset` 触发时，异步生成刚结束 session 的结构化摘要。\n\n## 行为\n\n- **异步执行**：hook 立即返回，摘要生成在后台，不阻塞命令响应\n- **降级策略**：LLM 不可用或生成失败时，写入规则摘要，不报错不中断\n- **文件格式**：`memory/YYYY-MM-DD-{slug}.md`，带 `<!-- summary-only -->` 标记\n\n## 摘要格式\n\n```markdown\n# Session: {date} {time}\n\n<!-- summary-only -->\n\n## 摘要\n## 主题\n{一句话概括，少于20字}\n\n## AI 决策模式\n{基于 scene/score/strategy 数据分析，1-3句描述}\n\n## 关键决策\n{决策列表，没有则写\"无明确决策\"}\n\n## 重要发现\n{发现列表，没有则写\"无\"}\n\n## 待跟进\n{待办列表，没有则写\"无\"}\n\n<!-- source: {sessionKey} -->\n```\n\n### AI 决策模式分析\n\n摘要 prompt 新增决策模式分析，从 ephemeral 的 v8 决策数据（scene、score、recommendedStrategy、risk factor）提炼：\n- 主要场景类型（clarify/task/troubleshoot/chat/...）\n- 复杂度评分分布\n- 推荐策略分布（DIRECT/STEP/SUBAGENT/PARALLEL/MEGA）\n- 风险意识表现\n- 互动风格（主动/被动/谨慎/大胆）\n\n## LLM 调用\n\n通过 v8 Router (3102) 调用 LLM 生成摘要，超时 20s。\n\n## Bootstrap 读取\n\nsession 启动时，扫描 `memory/` 下最新摘要文件（按修改时间），读入作为上下文。\n---","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776429055852}}
