{"type":"message","id":"e65053d2","parentId":"8845bb41","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:41:19.126Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway restarted successfully at 20:40:03. PID changed from 143081 to 149666. Now I need to think about the next step.\n\nStep: Verify the hook change is active and test the session-summary chain.\n\nWhat could go wrong:\n1. The hook file is read at startup, so the change should be active after restart\n2. But the session-summary hook is triggered on /new or /reset, not by the gateway directly\n3. I need to test if the hook works\n\nThe correct next step is to test the complete memory chain:\n1. Trigger a new session (/new)\n2. Check if a new session-summary is generated\n\n\n3. But wait - I should first verify the context API port 3101 is still working, since the session-summary hook reads from there and the context-api was stopped earlier\n\nActually, I need to reconsider the hook architecture. The session-summary hook is triggered by the gateway when /new or /reset is called, and it's defined in the HOOK.md metadata. The handler needs to read the previous session's messages, but I'm realizing the context API (3101) that the hook might depend on was previously running on 3106 - I need to verify this dependency chain is still intact after the restart.","thinkingSignature":"be68364f5515eaac6205d46d1242ad05820a6e84a1c21d2c87fdb6dfc19a9f7f"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\nGateway 已重启成功（PID 149666，20:40:03）。下一步需要验证 hook 改动是否生效，以及测试 session-summary 全链路。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n**session-summary hook 触发条件**：/new 或 /reset 时由 gateway 调用。测试方式：执行 /new 触发 hook，然后检查 memory/ 下是否有新文件。\n\n**但有一个风险**：handler.js 依赖读取 session 数据。旧版 HOOK.md 说\"从 context.previousSessionEntry.sessionFile 读取\"。这个字段由 gateway 注入，如果 gateway 重启后上下文注入逻辑变了，可能读不到 sessionFile。\n\n**验证顺序**：\n1. 先查 gateway 日志确认无报错\n2. 不执行 /new（会丢失当前会话），改为：检查现有的 session 文件路径是否可读\n3. 手动跑一个测试：调用 hook handler 的方式（或者检查 ephemeral 数据）\n\n**更安全的方案**：先确认 hook 文件语法无误，等用户下次自然 /new 时验证，而不是主动触发。\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n- handler.js 是 ESM 模块（import/export），systemd 运行方式下 Node.js 是否能正确加载？\n- gateway 重启后 session-file 路径注入是否还正常？\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n先检查 gateway 日志确认无报错，然后告知用户 hook 已更新，下次 /new 时会自动验证结果。\n</thinking>\n\nGateway 已重启成功（PID 149666）。现在需要验证 hook 改动是否正确加载：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_txmpxukiyb51_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 gateway 日志确认 hook 加载无报错\njournalctl --user -u openclaw-gateway.service -n 30 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"error|Error|hook|Hook|WARN\" | tail -15"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67099,"output":652,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89389,"cost":{"input":0.0201297,"output":0.0007823999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02221038}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429655093,"responseId":"06315d5740df7d0cf9fd9137745812ea"}}
