{"type":"message","id":"59a9e9c5","parentId":"ecf98828","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:41:34.623Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No errors in the gateway log. Good. Now let me think about what to do next.\n\nThe session-summary hook is an ESM module. When gateway loads hooks, it needs to handle ESM properly. Let me check if the hook was actually loaded.\n\nAlso, I should check if the hook changes are actually working. The next natural step would be to wait for the user to do /new, or I can manually test the hook handler.\n\nBut wait - I shouldn't just say \"this will work next time\". According to SOUL.md, I should verify and not leave things uncertain.\n\nLet me think about what I can check right now without disrupting the session:\n\n\nI can verify the hook file syntax is valid and check the session file path resolution logic, though the hook won't actually trigger until /new happens. Rather than trying to manually invoke the hook or asking the user to reset (which would lose the current conversation), I should confirm the hook file is syntactically sound and explain what happens next.","thinkingSignature":"beaf6606607e376d474abe821fb92844f5ed7f96e6e803e6e691a0778165b3eb"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n验证 hook 改动是否被 gateway 正确加载，同时不丢失当前 session。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n**当前 session-summary hook 是 ESM 模块**（import/export），gateway 通过动态 import() 加载。需要确认：\n1. gateway 是否成功加载了这个 ESM hook\n2. hook 的路径解析是否正确\n\n**测试 hook 的最安全方式**：手动验证 handler.js 的 ESM 语法 + 检查 hook 注册状态，而不是执行 /new。\n\n**执行 /new 的风险**：会丢失当前所有上下文。\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n- gateway 加载 hook 的日志没有输出，不代表成功也不代表失败\n- 我可以检查 hook 文件是否存在且语法正确\n- 最关键的是：handler.js 改了 URL，但这是运行时调用，不影响加载\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n检查 gateway 是否真的加载了 hook（查看日志），然后说明 hook 改动已生效，下次 /new 时自动验证。\n</think>\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sn6mnryfzfcl_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 gateway 是否识别并加载了 session-summary hook\njournalctl --user -u openclaw-gateway.service -n 50 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"session-summary\\|hook\\|load\" | tail -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":67769,"output":482,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89889,"cost":{"input":0.0203307,"output":0.0005784,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02220738}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429679589,"responseId":"06315d6d62fe89dd6ef03f6fc387f2b4"}}
