{"type":"message","id":"e479befb","parentId":"db52b18b","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:45:17.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Neither script has authorization code. So the 401 error must be coming from somewhere else. Let me check the actual cron job run more carefully. The cron runs an `agentTurn` which is an isolated session that runs an LLM agent. The agent's message is to run the script and append output to log.md. But the error says \"login fail\" - this might be from the isolated agent session trying to use some LLM API that's not authenticated.\n\nLet me look at the cron job definition more carefully. The message says:\n```\n执行 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/wiki-learn-once.sh 并将输出追加到 ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log.md\n\n\n```\n\nThis is an `agentTurn` payload, which runs an LLM agent. The agent would need an LLM API to run the script. The 401 error is probably the agent's LLM call failing - the API key for the LLM being used in the isolated session isn't working. Let me check the wiki-learn-once.sh script more carefully to see if it's doing something that would require LLM API access.\n\nActually, the `agentTurn` runs a full LLM agent, and that agent tries to execute the bash script. But the bash script itself doesn't call any LLMs. So the 401 is from the LLM itself during the agent's reasoning step - the agent Turn is using an LLM API that needs authentication. The error message says \"Please carry the API secret key in the 'Authorization' field of the request header\" - this sounds like a Feishu/Lark API, but the wiki scripts don't use that. This might be from a tool call the LLM agent makes during its reasoning.\n\n```","thinkingSignature":"21d8c68e247b04626668d77a1d603105a3d5469e18773948a00cd1721d36377a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y75dujv60q8h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 cron 最近一次运行的详细日志\ncron_id=\"b3c6834e-c671-4b21-b6d4-0dc9c86f0e84\"\ncron action=\"runs\"\ncron jobId=\"$cron_id\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"cron runs failed\"\n\n# 同时检查 wiki-learn 脚本实际在做什么（是否依赖外部 API）\nhead -5 ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log.md 2>/dev/null\necho \"---\"\ntail -20 ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/log.md 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"wiki\\|error\\|401\\|auth\" | tail -10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":71415,"output":506,"cacheRead":21638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93559,"cost":{"input":0.0214245,"output":0.0006072,"cacheRead":0.00129828,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023329979999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776429901465,"responseId":"06315e4ba4e9aeaafd1330715f127913"}}
